<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>EMA624_07_IH_0006</title>

		<!-- 공통 js-->
		<script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
		<script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

		<!-- 공통 css-->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

		<!-- 개별 -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema624_07.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_07_ih_0006">
			<section class="title type2">
				<h2 data-head="6_deep_green" class="is_star" lang="y">
					학생 수가 1반은 21명, 2반은 14명일 때 색연필 105자루를 반별 학생 수의 비에 따라 나누어 가지려고
					합니다. 두 반이 나누어 가지는 색연필은 각각 몇 자루인지 구해 보세요.
				</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents">
				<div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
					<div class="input_area">
						<div class="flex align_center">
							<span lang="y">1반</span>
							<span class="input_wrap">
								<math-field data-answer-single="63"></math-field>
							</span>
							<span lang="y">자루</span>
						</div>
						<div class="flex align_center">
							<span lang="y">2반</span>
							<span class="input_wrap">
								<math-field data-answer-single="42"></math-field>
							</span>
							<span lang="y">자루</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<!-- 해설 -->
				<div class="solve_area">
					<div class="inner_solve">
						<div class="flex">
							<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
							<div class="conts_solve">
								<p>색연필 105자루를 1반의 학생 수와 2반의 학생 수의 비 21 : 14로 나눕니다.</p>
								<p>1반: 105 × <span class="fraction_box"><span>21</span><span>21+14</span></span>
								  <span class="eq-middle">=</span> 105 × <span class="fraction_box"><span>21</span><span>35</span></span>
								  <span class="eq-middle">=</span> 63(자루)
								</p>
								<p>2반: 105 × <span class="fraction_box"><span>14</span><span>21+14</span></span>
								  <span class="eq-middle">=</span> 105 × <span class="fraction_box"><span>14</span><span>35</span></span>
								  <span class="eq-middle">=</span> 42(자루)
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="btn_area">
					<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
					<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
					<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
